TY  - JOUR
AU  - Wilson, Carol
AU  - Taylor, Emma
TI  - Deep Learning in Medical Image Analysis: Current Trends and Future Directions
JO  - Medical Image Analysis
VL  - 67
SP  - 102089
PY  - 2023
DO  - 10.1016/j.media.2023.102089
AB  - Medical image analysis has been revolutionized by deep learning techniques. This systematic review analyzes 200 papers from 2019-2023 focusing on convolutional neural networks, transformers, and generative models. We found that deep learning achieves state-of-the-art performance in radiology, pathology, and ophthalmology applications.
